<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id620e41f4-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s16"><num value="16">§ 16.</num><heading> Transportation of Indians in Bureau vehicles</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">On and after <date date="1984-10-12">October 12, 1984</date>, passenger carrying motor vehicles of the Bureau of Indian Affairs may be used for the transportation of Indians.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id620e41f5-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/98/473/tI/s101/c/tI/s100">Pub. L. 98–473, title I, § 101(c) [title I, § 100]</ref>, <date date="1984-10-12">Oct. 12, 1984</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/98/1837">98 Stat. 1837</ref>, 1850.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
